# Design Systems A/B

Tokens live in `apps/web/app/globals.css` under `[data-theme='gift'|'creator']`. Layouts set the attribute (`(gift)/layout.tsx`, `(creator)/layout.tsx`). Prefer `var(--primary)` / `var(--background)` — don’t hardcode the other theme’s hex into a route.

## Soft Gift (`gift`)

| Token | Role |
|---|---|
| `--inabiya-pink` `#FF6B9D` | Primary CTA |
| `--inabiya-soft` `#FFF3F8` | Page bg |
| `--inabiya-heading` `#2D2640` | Display text |
| Fonts | Fraunces (display) + Plus Jakarta Sans (body) |

Surfaces: storefront, blog, commerce/editorial/platform admin.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD — hardcoded pink (seen in some MVP pages); breaks theme + dark-text contrast work
className="bg-[#FF6B9D]"

// ✅ GOOD
className="bg-[var(--primary)] text-[var(--primary-foreground)]"
```

## Creator (`creator`)

Forest/cream/terracotta via HSL CSS vars. Fonts: Playfair Display + Manrope. Never Soft Gift pink on these trees.

## Never

- Mix themes on one route tree
- Treat medical `SpecialistProfile` as marketplace creators
- Inter/Roboto/Arial as brand · emoji icons · purple-glow SaaS heroes · hero sticker overlays
- A third palette without `Design.md` + ADR

## Interaction

`data-testid` kebab-case on critical controls. Tap targets ≥ 48px (primary CTAs ~56px). Soft Gift motion: calm 0.2–0.6s GSAP — see `15-gsap-motion`.
